ing are to 1) model the test set-ups and reproduce the measurements (as a\nvalidation of the modeling), 2) determine the origin of the non-common path\nerrors, and 3) propose modifications to the current metrology design to reach\nthe required 1nm stability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jul 2014 18:00:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-07"}
