otropic luminosity, we detected the methanol maser\nsources brighter than ~5x1025 erg/s from our unbiased survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2014 02:02:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
